Moving in with your boyfriend is one of the last rites of passage on the way to becoming a fully-fledged grown-up.But, when it comes to shacking up with your significant other, things suddenly get real.Sharing your home with a romantic partner changes your relationship and after that initial period of excitement, some pretty weird things can start to happen.Now, us girls can get a pretty bad rap for clogging up the plughole with our hair, but you ll soon find that it works both ways.The pain of cleaning up what feels like endless bits of facial hair will start to feel like a relative past time because we can almost guarantee that your bathroom sink will be permanently covered in beard trimmings.It will congregate everywhere, and you will never be able to keep on top of it &#8211; just when you think you&#8217;ve cleared it, you spot more.&nbsp;